\b\fs28 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa120

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 Psychoanalysts are split in the classical (Freudian), Jungian and unspecified.  The game contains a number of independent psychiatrists who, while they are familiar with psychoanalysis, are not professed members of the faction.
